                          <h4 class="alt-font post-title font-weight-600 text-white display-block margin-5px-bottom">$1 Million Grant to Advance Racial Equity</h4>
                          <div class="author">
                              <span class="text-white text-uppercase text-extra-small display-inline-block alt-font-3">March 2018</span>
                          </div>
                          <div class="separator-line-horrizontal-full bg-medium-gray margin-seven-tb md-margin-four-tb"></div>
                          <p class="text-white">Through a partnership with Lumina Foundation and Rockefeller Philanthropy Advisors, the Center received $1 million to support two resources that help advance racial equity in higher education: The National Assessment of Collegiate Campus Climates (NACCC) and the USC Equity Institutes.</p>
                      </div>
