                            <%= image_tag("https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F40219660%2F142565338226%2F1%2Foriginal.jpg?w=1000&rect=0%2C0%2C9000%2C4500&s=67310925a9c32416d80f485624104660")%>
                          </a>
                          <div class="blog-categories bg-white text-black text-uppercase text-extra-small alt-font-3">event</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="post-details padding-30px-all bg-red sm-padding-20px-all">
                          <div class="blog-hover-color"></div>
                          <h4 class="alt-font post-title font-weight-600 text-white display-block margin-5px-bottom">Convening on Gay Latino Men in College</h4>
                          <div class="author">
                              <span class="text-white text-uppercase text-extra-small display-inline-block alt-font-3">February 2018</span>
                          </div>
                          <div class="separator-line-horrizontal-full bg-medium-gray margin-seven-tb md-margin-four-tb"></div>
                          <p class="text-white">Oscar Patrón, a research associate in the Center, has amassed considerable expertise on the needs and experiences of gay Latino men attending U.S. colleges and universities. In February, he and Shaun Harper organized a summit that brought several dozen undergraduates, graduate students, and recent college graduates to USC. Most came from community colleges and four-year institutions in California and Arizona. One came from Virginia to participate in the event. </p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </li>
              <!-- end post item -->
              <!-- start post item -->
              <li class="grid-item wow fadeInUp last-paragraph-no-margin">
