                          <div class="separator-line-horrizontal-full bg-medium-gray margin-seven-tb md-margin-four-tb"></div>
                          <p class="text-white">In Fall 2017, the Center’s founder and executive director was formally installed as the Clifford and Betty Allen Chair in Urban Leadership. Harper was also named a Provost Professor in the Rossier School of Education and the Marshall School of Business. USC’s 18 Provost Professors are exceptional interdisciplinary scholars who hold appointments in two or more academic schools.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </li>
              <!-- end post item -->
              <!-- start post item -->
              <li class="grid-item wow fadeInUp last-paragraph-no-margin">
