                              <span class="text-white text-uppercase text-extra-small display-inline-block alt-font-3">October 2017</span>
                          </div>
                          <div class="separator-line-horrizontal-full bg-medium-gray margin-seven-tb md-margin-four-tb"></div>
                          <p class="text-white">The Center joined with Asian Americans, Pacific Islanders, and committed others across the country to resist xenophobia, Islamophobia, hate speech, and racist immigration policies during the AAPI National Week of Action on Immigration. Using the hashtag #AAPIequity, Sumun Pendakur organized a Twitter Town Hall that engaged people across the country.</p>
                      </div>
