                          <p class="text-white">As the Center’s new chief learning officer, Sumun L. Pendakur leads the USC Equity Institutes and a range of organizational change efforts. In her previous role as Assistant Vice President for Diversity and Inclusion at Harvey Mudd College, Pendakur was chief diversity officer and a member of the president’s cabinet.</p>
